{betah - s tmp, betah + s tmp} // Transpose // N\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"bb922344-90a4-4948-b1c1-259ad7d4ae63"],

Cell["\<\
cond := F <= InverseCDF[fdist, 1 - alpha]
confint := Reduce[cond]
A = Transpose[{{1, 0}}]; u = {beta0}; confint // N (* k = 0 *)
A = Transpose[{{0, 1}}]; u = {beta1}; confint // N (* k = 1 *)\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"3dde5c35-c569-4bb1-b917-38402a9d6bbe"],

Cell["\<\
