\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"dbae18b6-368f-440c-9dc9-245e0369fccc"],

Cell["Reduce[c1 a1 + c2 a2 == {0, 0}]", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"f14702fa-d871-4ddb-886f-76b374867008"],

Cell["\<\
